00:00:59.823 --> 00:01:03.848
and we get the answer as 352.

00:01:09.540 --> 00:01:11.296
That's it.

00:01:11.296 --> 00:01:12.573
Let's try another sum.

00:01:12.573 --> 00:01:14.896
45 times 11.

00:01:14.896 --> 00:01:16.358
Let's hear it.

00:01:16.358 --> 00:01:20.576
Exactly, that's 495.

00:01:20.576 --> 00:01:23.943
And 75 times 11.

00:01:25.636 --> 00:01:28.182
So it gives you 7,125,

00:01:28.182 --> 00:01:33.364
