00:03:33.828 --> 00:03:35.114
-003.

00:03:35.114 --> 00:03:37.830
We go crosswise like this,

00:03:37.830 --> 00:03:41.787
and we get 996 minus 003 would give us

00:03:42.910 --> 00:03:44.135
993,

00:03:44.135 --> 00:03:47.610
and 004 times 003 would give us

00:03:47.610 --> 00:03:48.890
012.

00:03:48.890 --> 00:03:51.302
And that's our answer.

00:03:58.738 --> 00:03:59.969
Thank you.

