00:08:15.085 --> 00:08:16.576
[6],

00:08:16.576 --> 00:08:17.721
and 1 times 1 gives us

00:08:17.721 --> 00:08:18.791
[1].

00:08:18.791 --> 00:08:19.532
6 plus 1,

00:08:19.532 --> 00:08:20.451
[7].

00:08:22.005 --> 00:08:23.667
1 times 3 gives us

00:08:23.667 --> 00:08:25.210
[3].

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:28.116
And that's it, and that's our answer.

00:08:36.315 --> 00:08:39.282
No more tedious calculations,

00:08:39.282 --> 00:08:41.454
no more going through the rough work,

00:08:41.454 --> 00:08:43.919
it's simple in one line.

